CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Westlake Chemical Partners LP is a part of the chemical industry in the United States. Through its operating interests in Westlake Chemical OpCo LP (OpCo), it acquires ethyelene production facilities, which primarily convert ethane into ethylene. OpCo sells ethylene and its co-products such as propylene, crude butadiene, pyrolysis gasoline, and hydrogen to Westlake and other customers located in the United States.
